<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>ETHIOPIAN E-VOTING SYSTEM</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700;800;900&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #0D3B2E;
            --secondary: #1E6B52;
            --accent: #FCD116;
            --accent2: #DA121A;
            --light: #F8F9FA;
            --text-light: #FFFFFF;
            --text-dark: #2D3748;
            --border-radius: 16px;
            --box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            --transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d3557 0%, #457b9d 25%, #a8dadc 50%, #f1faee 75%, #ffffff 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(232, 65, 24, 0.08) 0%, transparent 40%),
                            radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(20, 126, 59, 0.08) 0%, transparent 40%),
                            radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
                            linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 48%, rgba(29, 53, 87, 0.03) 50%, transparent 52%);
            z-index: -2;
            animation: backgroundShift 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes backgroundShift {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-10px) translateY(-10px); }
        }

        .header {
            background: rgba(13, 59, 46, 0.95);
            padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #078930 33%, #FCD116 33% 66%, #DA121A 66%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: logoPulse 3s infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes logoPulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .hero {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 1000px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            background: rgba(13, 59, 46, 0.7);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            animation: slideInDown 1s ease-out;
        }

        @@keyframes slideInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .hero h1 .highlight {
            color: var(--accent);
            display: block;
            font-size: 5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ffd700);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            animation: colorShift 3s infinite alternate;
        }

        @@keyframes colorShift {
            0% { filter: hue-rotate(0deg); }
            100% { filter: hue-rotate(20deg); }
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            animation: slideInUp 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
        }

        @@keyframes slideInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
        }

        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .stat-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            min-width: 180px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .stat-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .features {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
        }

        .features-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 120px;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--light);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13, 59, 46, 0.03), rgba(30, 107, 82, 0.05));
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover .feature-icon {
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .process {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .process-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .process .section-title {
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .process .section-subtitle {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .process-steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .process-steps::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 60px;
            left: 10%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border: 5px solid var(--light);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .step:hover .step-number {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .step-content {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 250px;
        }

        .step-content h3 {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .step-content p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 500;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary), var(--primary));
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            background: #e6b800;
        }

        /* Animation classes */
        .fade-in {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
        }

        .fade-in.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        .pulse {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @@keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Media Queries */
        @@media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero h1 .highlight {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .nav-links {
                gap: 1rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .hero-content {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
            
            .hero h1 .highlight {
                font-size: 3.2rem;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .hero-stats {
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .stat-item {
                min-width: 140px;
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }

            .process-steps {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 3rem;
            }

            .process-steps::before {
                display: none;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 350px;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .feature-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .hero h1 .highlight {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .stat-item {
                min-width: 120px;
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <nav class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">EVS</div>
                <div class="logo-text">ETHIOPIAN E-VOTING SYSTEM</div>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> HOME</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Home/About"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> ABOUT</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Home/Contact"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> CONTACT</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Home/Login"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> LOGIN</a></li>
                <li><a href="/Home/Register"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> REGISTER</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>SECURE DIGITAL VOTING <span class="highlight">FOR ETHIOPIA</span></h1>
            <p>EMPOWERING EVERY ETHIOPIAN CITIZEN WITH A MODERN, TRANSPARENT, AND ACCESSIBLE VOTING PLATFORM FOR THE 21ST CENTURY</p>
            
            <div class="hero-stats">
                <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                    <div class="stat-number">99.9%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">SYSTEM UPTIME</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                    <div class="stat-number">12M+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">REGISTERED VOTERS</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item fade-in">
                    <div class="stat-number">256-BIT</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">ENCRYPTION</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="features-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">WHY OUR E-VOTING SYSTEM?</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">DESIGNED SPECIFICALLY FOR ETHIOPIA'S UNIQUE NEEDS WITH CUTTING-EDGE TECHNOLOGY AND MAXIMUM SECURITY</p>
            
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>MILITARY-GRADE SECURITY</h3>
                    <p>END-TO-END ENCRYPTION AND BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY ENSURE YOUR VOTE IS COMPLETELY SECURE, ANONYMOUS, AND TAMPER-PROOF</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>ACCESSIBLE ANYWHERE</h3>
                    <p>VOTE FROM ANY DEVICE WITH INTERNET CONNECTION - MAKING DEMOCRACY ACCESSIBLE TO ALL ETHIOPIANS ACROSS THE NATION</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>INSTANT RESULTS</h3>
                    <p>REAL-TIME VOTE COUNTING AND IMMEDIATE, VERIFIABLE RESULT PUBLICATION AFTER VOTING CLOSES</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>IDENTITY VERIFICATION</h3>
                    <p>ADVANCED ID VERIFICATION USING ETHIOPIAN NATIONAL IDS AND OPTIONAL BIOMETRIC TECHNOLOGY TO PREVENT FRAUD</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>TRANSPARENT PROCESS</h3>
                    <p>COMPLETE AUDIT TRAIL AND TRANSPARENT VOTING PROCESS THAT EVERYONE CAN VERIFY AND TRUST</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>SUPPORT ILLETRATE VOTER</h3>
                    <p>ILLETRATE VOTER ARE INCLUDED IN OUR SYSTEM BECAUSE THEY ARE THE MEMBER OF THE COUNTRY</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Voting Process Section -->
    <section class="process">
        <div class="process-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">HOW TO VOTE</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">OUR STREAMLINED PROCESS MAKES VOTING SIMPLE, SECURE, AND ACCESSIBLE FOR EVERY ELIGIBLE ETHIOPIAN CITIZEN</p>
            
            <div class="process-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>VERIFY</h3>
                        <p>COMPLETE IDENTITY VERIFICATION THROUGH OUR SECURE AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>REGISTER</h3>
                        <p>CREATE YOUR ACCOUNT WITH YOUR ETHIOPIAN NATIONAL ID AND PERSONAL DETAILS</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>VOTE</h3>
                        <p>CAST THE CANDIDATE YOU NEED DURING THE OFFICIAL VOTING PERIOD</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>VIEW RESULT</h3>
                        <p>THE VOTER CAN VIEW RESULT TO KNOW THEIR REPRESENTATIVE</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-container">
            <h2>READY TO PARTICIPATE IN ETHIOPIA'S DIGITAL DEMOCRACY?</h2>
            <p>JOIN MILLIONS OF ETHIOPIANS WHO ARE ALREADY USING OUR SECURE PLATFORM TO EXERCISE THEIR DEMOCRATIC RIGHTS</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="/Home/Login" class="btn btn-primary pulse">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> ACCESS VOTING PORTAL
                </a>
                <a href="/Home/About" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> LEARN MORE ABOUT THE SYSTEM
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        // Scroll animation for elements
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const fadeElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in');
            
            const fadeInOnScroll = function() {
                fadeElements.forEach(element => {
                    const elementTop = element.getBoundingClientRect().top;
                    const elementVisible = 150;
                    
                    if (elementTop < window.innerHeight - elementVisible) {
                        element.classList.add('visible');
                    }
                });
            };
            
            // Check on load
            fadeInOnScroll();
            
            // Check on scroll
            window.addEventListener('scroll', fadeInOnScroll);
        });

        // Smooth scrolling for anchor links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');
                if (targetId === '#') return;
                
                const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);
                if (targetElement) {
                    targetElement.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth'
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>